{"tid":1603222,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［是日有感］做個有危機意識的和理非","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T08:31:56.000Z","uid":27626,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"062c484114accb6299fb45a17dd866856a333bdb","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"發夢今日去咗灣仔行街<br />\n行到一半見到地鐵站口有火魔法<br />\n附近仲有另一個出口用垃圾桶塞住<br />\n係人都知灣仔站入面全部都係狗<br />\n啲人見到火魔法個刻好high<br />\n仲對住個地鐵站唱有班警察毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我幫手叫啲和理非快啲走<br />\n因為唔知啲狗幾時會衝上黎捉人<br />\n但佢地仲繼續唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一出火魔法<br />\n和理非就要有心理準備啲狗隨時出黎咬人<br />\n所以唔好掛住食花生要快啲走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路走一路將消息話比後面聽<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望大家出黎就算冇事發生都要危機意識</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔係會害死好多人</span></span>"},{"pid":"e5331c3f171b9f2bc0684b794a859d77c11f1681","tid":1603222,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:38:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6d8b8d2dbd949a19ba46274d8841d14fc874517","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:39:39.000Z","msg":"適當時候做適當既事"},{"pid":"f959e28625db74fda932a812baee01024058a42b","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:40:16.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"c6a8634eb191e9babda9a94942aa57c0bae75566","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"2ebc3ea6388d8faf885804862c68ea4a5a9dc9a0","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"82da1764e08f8097550046a1a689be53544e4a50","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:40:53.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"0784c8ab9f4113a9ba337b19a84f0e6a450930b3","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"60d0ce54a2c523c0ee68149f65ef2a19a7526007","tid":1603222,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1df06adeb5934f7c8fd2b6be5ea16744b6a4050a","tid":1603222,"uid":311907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"大家係咪唔記得好多野要繼續做？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602820</a>"},{"pid":"3eaad1908c61962feba6884d3f77b696b4b6be9c","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"aeee3bbc16b8217763903490503fe588576fd0bb","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"01fd370881365131921a136801b2ee136a65abb7","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"0d304aa9866001daffd03f086352a459fe299114","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"2fc12fc5c9a97a7122ebc8ab2028f9cc92211fb7","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"f1834aa42982041798ae43025726e1e55a0d484c","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:07.000Z","msg":"930 全港三罷變死城！"},{"pid":"006c0bcf33376331bfb0cc61f889ce3e5015d709","tid":1603222,"uid":259321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quot