=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8JoOj.png&h=2d0ace40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"4310507efac646e51dcb18a25bb7c858a331e3d3","tid":1603222,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"55f70167d1b02c3108dee8437e2b6bc957723d99","tid":1603222,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbcc2a800e69dfc424e3df4f825d0f072705c39a","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"要走都唔好亂跑！<br />\n人數係我地優勢呀！"},{"pid":"a9c9e87c1e094b4889246680d2bd1133d2a661ef","tid":1603222,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"一係幫手打，一係轉區"},{"pid":"5b89ff699f03d03279dae0148582a0770b6644e6","tid":1603222,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔打唔好上前線，唔打得就去第二區堵路，打游擊分散兵力</span>"},{"pid":"9125d2c2c3b00da30c1383473ca8acbccb166994","tid":1603222,"uid":207902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得好多人出來行街街<br />\n個危機意識好低<br />\n好認同樓主所講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d700e32e30b03711f343e149f1d3f919b1f84334","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"唱歌都要揀啱時間唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c473e249de2e7b8fc44e05f0a16b000519b2730","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9125d2c2c3b00da30c1383473ca8acbccb166994","tid":1603222,"uid":207902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得好多人出來行街街<br />\n個危機意識好低<br />\n好認同樓主所講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.