":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"唔止今日，琴日已經想屌<br />\n喺金鐘撤離嗰陣<br />\n一邊行大街，一邊叫口號<br />\n慌死啲狗唔知你哋喺邊<br />\n如果有狗衝埋嚟，成班黑衫個個得個衛生口罩<br />\n隨時team kill<br />\n大佬呀，你宜家唔係遊行，係撤離<br />\n醒少少啦<br />\nBe water精髓係無形無色<br />\n唔可以俾人咁容易捉到<br />\n下次唔該改進"},{"pid":"04f2ab286dfd064507ee585ea3004a75920f64f5","tid":1603222,"uid":103363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"呢D 時間仲唱歌真係要幾戇鳩先諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉.........睇路啦仲唱"},{"pid":"3de52e2eec999532505f4423e8e9c89fce00dc00","tid":1603222,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea87040d03b60313bb6ce0838fccdcefb933adf9","tid":1603222,"uid":78356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0a07da3c30234e2c70f6685e266dfcaf3ba01c","tid":1603222,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"和理非三寶:<br />\n雀巢咖啡 鎖頭 玻璃樽"},{"pid":"269c49ec01360d36d9265a89739660c449be62a7","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"危機感好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d7d1076123d51df1d9d6c93b970bfd508ecb9d","tid":1603222,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"聽日大三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0471f3a47f05c928266306658259223fdb818690","tid":1603222,"uid":16846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"到底佢哋係準備代坐48定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><